# System Architecture Document

## High-Level Flow
User → Gradio UI → Prompt Orchestration → LLM API → Streaming Output → UI

## Layers

### 1. Presentation Layer
- Gradio ChatInterface
- Parameter sliders
- OAuth login

### 2. Application Layer
- `respond()` function
- Message formatting
- Context management
- Parameter injection

### 3. Model Layer
- LLM accessed via Inference API
- Streaming token generation

### 4. Deployment Layer
- Cloud-hosted web application
- Secure token-based authentication
